Very nice but very bad hotspot. Everything takes forever to load.
Two toilets.

campspots.name: Penrose Commons OHV

Hotspot internet is great. Had a video call with 28 people.

Secluded, but less open in terms of getting a wide view.

Rocky roads

campspots.notes:
Secluded even if it's next to the road. Great hotspot 29/7.

Motocross and ATV going around sometimes, especialy weekends, not so many on weekdays.

campspots.name: Woodland Park
campspots.notes: Great spot, great view, usually great hotspot signal, sometimes slow, but usually recovers after 0-60 minutes.

campspots.name: Woodridge Primitive Park
campspots.notes: Very bad hotspot. Everything takes forever to load. Nice for camping but not really vanlife. Vehicles must park and can not go on grass. It's like a rest area but for camping.
